OL,3,CLegendary ITV News presenter Sandy
OL,4,CGall dies aged 97
OL,6,FITV News Europe Editor James Mates
OL,7,Flooks back at Sandy Gall's legendary
OL,8,Fcareer.
OL,10,FThe veteran broadcaster and journalist
OL,11,FSandy Gall has died aged 97, his
OL,12,Ffamily has confirmed.
OL,14,FGall became one of the most familiar
OL,15,Ffaces in the country, firstly as a
OL,16,Fforeign correspondent for ITN, before
OL,17,Fbecoming co-presenter of News at Ten.
