OL,3,CLegendary ITV News presenter Sandy
OL,4,CGall dies aged 97
OL,6,FHis family revealed he died at his
OL,7,Fhome in Kent on Sunday, and paid
OL,8,Ftribute to him saying: "His was a
OL,9,Fgreat life, generously and
OL,10,Fcourageously lived."
OL,12,FGall's career in journalism spanned
OL,13,Fmore than 50 years, starting in 1952
OL,14,Fwhen he joined the Aberdeen Press and
OL,15,FJournal.
OL,17,FHe then worked at Reuters news agency
OL,18,Ffor ten years as a foreign
OL,19,Fcorrespondent, before joining ITN in
OL,20,F1963.
