OL,3,CLegendary ITV News presenter Sandy
OL,4,CGall dies aged 97
OL,6,FIt was at ITN where he was to become a
OL,7,Fhousehold name in the UK, until his
OL,8,Fretirement from the broadcaster in
OL,9,F1992.
OL,11,FOne of his first assignments with ITN
OL,12,Fwas in Dallas, Texas just hours after
OL,13,Fthe assassination of President Kennedy.
OL,15,FHis time at ITN saw him cover some of
OL,16,Fthe 20th century's biggest stories,
OL,17,Fsuch as the Vietnam War, the Soviet-
OL,18,FAfghan War and America's civil rights
OL,19,Fmovement, where he interviewed Martin
OL,20,FLuther King in 1965.
