OL,3,CLegendary ITV News presenter Sandy
OL,4,CGall dies aged 97
OL,6,FHe was also one of the few journalists
OL,7,Fto remain in Vietnam after the victory
OL,8,Fof the North Vietnamese to cover the
OL,9,Ffall of Saigon in 1975.
OL,11,FGall went on to co-present News At Ten
OL,12,Fin 1970, which was then the UK's most
OL,13,Fwatched news programme.
OL,15,FHe made his final presenting
OL,16,Fappearance on News at Ten in 1991,
OL,17,Fbefore returning to work with the
OL,18,Fcompany as a special reporter until
OL,19,Fhis final retirement in 1992.
