OL,3,CLegendary ITV News presenter Sandy
OL,4,CGall dies aged 97
OL,6,FHe later became the founder and
OL,7,Fchairman of Sandy Gall's Afghanistan
OL,8,FAppeal, a charity for disabled Afghans
OL,9,Fthat ran for nearly 40 years. It began
OL,10,Fwith a focus on treating Afghans with
OL,11,Fwar-related casualties and land mine
OL,12,Fvictims, as well as children in
OL,13,Frefugee camps.
OL,15,FThis focus widened, as the
OL,16,Frehabilitation needs of many other
OL,17,Fpeople with disabilities became
OL,18,Fapparent.
